In your controller, you can make a new array out of `list`:

    let newList = [];
    let tempList = [];
    for (let i=0; i&lt;list.length; i++) {
        tempList.push(list[i]);
        if (i%9 === 0) {
            newList.push(tempList);
            tempList = [];
        }
    }

`newList` will be like this:

